<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-008/AC-001> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/updated_at> "2026-06-16T09:24:27.44796Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-008/AC-001> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/belongs_to_project> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/proj-default> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-008/AC-001> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "  - [ ] AC-001: 每内置主题须注册 ≥ 1 份预设变体（template），通过 `defineTheme.templates` 字段或独立 `defineTemplate({ themeId, templateId, render })` API 注册。**创建文档时**从 template 一次性拷贝预填 Markdown 内容到编辑器；frontmatter `template` 字段为元数据/审计标记，渲染管线不消费此字段。" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-008/AC-001> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/entity_id> "AC-001" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/F-008/AC-001> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/AcceptanceCriteria> .
