<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-018%3A%20POST%20/api/v1/wechat-assets/upload> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-018: POST /api/v1/wechat-assets/upload\n\n```yaml\npath: /api/v1/wechat-assets/upload\nmethod: POST\nmodule: M-010\nmaps_to: F-005 AC-003\nauth: API key (Bearer Header)\nrequest:\n  headers:\n    Authorization: { type: string, required: true }\n    Idempotency-Key: { type: string, required: false }\n  body:\n    imageUrl: { type: string, required: true, desc: \"通常来自 /images/upload 上传结果\" }\n    type: { type: \"'image'|'voice'|'video'|'thumb'\", required: true }\nresponse:\n  202:\n    schema: |\n      z.object({\n        jobId: z.string().uuid(),\n        statusUrl: z.string().url(),  // 形如 /api/v1/jobs/{jobId}\n      })\n  401: { schema: ErrorResponse }\n  502: { schema: ErrorResponse, desc: \"微信素材库 API 上游错误\" }\n```" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-018%3A%20POST%20/api/v1/wechat-assets/upload> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
