<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/5.1%20%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "340999e2c8030a316c141ede8d1b2c43c5af859ea0fee416b7b81314e377678c" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/5.1%20%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000009" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/5.1%20%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 5.1 性能\n\n| 场景 | 目标 (PRD §3.1) | 架构机制 |\n|------|----------------|----------|\n| 万字键入延迟 P95 < 50ms | 编辑器响应 | 增量解析（CodeMirror 6 syntax tree 增量更新）+ 渲染管线增量执行（mdast diff 驱动，仅重渲染受影响子树）+ Vapor Mode 命令式 DOM 更新 |\n| 主题切换 < 200ms | 重跑后段管线 | 主题切换不重跑 mdast 解析，仅重跑 `hast → pre-paste → post-paste → inline-styled HTML`；token 字典预编译为 CSS-in-JS 字面量映射 |\n| MCP `render_markdown` 冷启动 P95 < 800ms | 万字稿件 | 渲染核心 `@wechat-flow/core` lazy import + pack 按需加载 + Edge runtime 部署形态时 V8 isolate < 50ms 冷启 |\n| 视觉回归 CI 时长 | 不阻塞 PR | Turborepo affected 检测 + 远程缓存，仅 fixture / 主题受影响时跑对应子矩阵 |" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/5.1%20%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/5.1%20%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/sort_key> "5.1 性能" .
