<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "2faafffd2dcce7a009bcc2834b16a37d5596b9c17bc02567d29823300af28ece" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000009" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/F-009%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8C%85> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### F-009: 主题继承与品牌包\n\n- **用户故事**: 作为企业/组织管理员，我希望在内置主题基础上派生并锁定品牌配色与字体，以便确保多作者发布的内容视觉风格统一。\n- **验收标准**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 支持主题继承：父主题 + delta 模式，组织可在内置主题基础上派生定制主题，无需复制完整 token 字典。\n  - [ ] AC-002: 支持品牌包：企业可在主题之上锁定字体、配色、组件子集，产出受控写作环境。\n- **优先级**: P2\n- **备注**: 与 F-003 单文档级 `paint` 覆盖正交——paint 是写作者个人单文档行为，品牌包是组织级配色字体子集锁定。\n\n---" .
