<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-038%3A%20M-009%20list_themes%20/%20describe_theme%20/%20list_blocks%20/%20describe_block%20Tool> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "dev-plan" .
