<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.4%20%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "ui-spec" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.4%20%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "04d8c77e1cf16b0af3797e158c1e34378ec199e3898b86fa5b8267730e3d830c" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.4%20%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000023" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.4%20%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 1.4 阴影与层叠 Token\n\n| Token | 值 | 用途 |\n|-------|----|------|\n| `--shadow-sm` | `0 1px 3px rgba(28,25,23,0.08)` | 卡片轻微浮起感 |\n| `--shadow-base` | `0 2px 8px rgba(28,25,23,0.10)` | 下拉菜单、Popover |\n| `--shadow-md` | `0 4px 16px rgba(28,25,23,0.12)` | Modal、Command Palette |\n| `--shadow-lg` | `0 8px 32px rgba(28,25,23,0.16)` | 大型浮层 |\n\n层叠顺序（z-index）：\n\n| Token | 值 | 层级说明 |\n|-------|----|----------|\n| `--z-splitter` | `10` | 栏宽拖拽 handle |\n| `--z-toolbar` | `20` | 顶栏 |\n| `--z-dropdown` | `100` | 下拉菜单、Popover |\n| `--z-mobile-bar` | `150` | 移动端底部固定栏（介于 toolbar 和 dropdown 之间，确保 Modal/BottomSheet 可覆盖） |\n| `--z-modal` | `300` | Modal、Dialog（含 P-002 移动底部抽屉）|\n| `--z-command` | `400` | Command Palette（覆盖 Modal 以上） |\n| `--z-toast` | `500` | Toast 通知（始终在最顶，含从移动端固定栏上方升起的 copy-success Toast）|" .
