<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/1.1%20%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000001" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/1.1%20%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 1.1 项目类型\n\n**类型**: fullstack\n\n包含浏览器编辑器（Vue 3.5 SPA + Vite）、Hono BFF / 中继 / MCP HTTP server、Node 端 MCP stdio server、CLI、可热加载主题/插件 pack 体系。所有形态共享同一份 framework-agnostic 渲染核心包 `@wechat-flow/core`。" .
