<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-003%3A%20list_themes> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-003: list_themes\n\n```yaml\ntool: list_themes\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002\nrequest: {}\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    themes: { type: \"ThemeSummary[]\", desc: \"{id, name, description, version, scene}[]\" }\n```" .
