<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.1%20%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Surface%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000008" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.1%20%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Surface%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### 1.1.1 表面色（Surface）\n\n| Token | 值 | 用途 |\n|-------|----|------|\n| `--color-surface` | `#FAF8F5` | 主底色、编辑器背景 |\n| `--color-surface-elevated` | `#F4F1EC` | 左侧面板背景（比编辑器略深，暗示功能区） |\n| `--color-surface-overlay` | `#EDEAE3` | 悬停项背景、激活菜单项 |\n| `--color-surface-sunken` | `#E7E3DA` | 输入框背景（低于周围层级） |\n| `--color-surface-preview` | `#F7F7F7` | 右侧预览面板底色（模拟微信默认白底，略冷以区分编辑区） |" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.1%20%E8%A1%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Surface%EF%BC%89> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
