<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.3%20%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Text%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/part_of_document> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.3%20%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Text%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_level> "4" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.1.3%20%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E8%89%B2%EF%BC%88Text%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/section_anchor> "1.1.3 文字色（Text）" .
