<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-048%3A%20M-007%20plugin-api%20surface%EF%BC%88defineBlock/defineVariant/defineRule/defineTheme%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "dev-plan" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-048%3A%20M-007%20plugin-api%20surface%EF%BC%88defineBlock/defineVariant/defineRule/defineTheme%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "495c4fdece20b491da4a2616215483dd93077d6c389c894c1883b8a609f0f8ca" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-048%3A%20M-007%20plugin-api%20surface%EF%BC%88defineBlock/defineVariant/defineRule/defineTheme%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000007" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-048%3A%20M-007%20plugin-api%20surface%EF%BC%88defineBlock/defineVariant/defineRule/defineTheme%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### T-048: M-007 plugin-api surface（defineBlock/defineVariant/defineRule/defineTheme）\n\n- **目标**: 实现 plugin-api surface（沙箱内白名单 API）：`defineBlock`、`defineVariant`、`defineRule`、`defineTheme`、`registerAsset`\n- **模块**: M-007 (插件沙箱与 plugin-api)\n- **task_kind**: feature\n- **priority**: P1\n- **complexity**: medium\n- **sprint**: 5\n- **tdd_mode**: light\n- **tdd_acceptance**: all\n- **tdd_refactor**: auto\n- **security_sensitive**: false\n- **dependencies**: [T-047, T-020]\n- **acceptance_criteria**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: Given 插件沙箱内调用 `defineBlock({ id: 'my-block', attrsSchema: z.object({...}), render: () => '...' })`，When 执行（通过 Comlink RPC），Then 主线程 M-005 Block 注册中心可通过 `describeBlock('my-block')` 查到该 Block\n  - [ ] AC-002: Given `defineVariant({ blockId: 'callout', id: 'my-variant', render: () => '...' })`，When 执行，Then `listBlockVariants('callout')` 返回含 `my-variant` [F-010 AC-006]\n  - [ ] AC-003: Given manifest 声明 variant 注册意图但实际未调用 `defineVariant`，When plugin 加载完成，When `manifest-check` 验证，Then 产生 `E_MANIFEST_VARIANT_MISMATCH` warning\n- **deliverables**:\n  - [ ] `packages/plugin-api/src/surface/plugin-api.ts` — `defineBlock` / `defineVariant` / `defineRule` / `defineTheme` / `registerAsset` / `requestResource` API [ARCH#§2.M-007]\n  - [ ] 更新 `packages/plugin-api/src/validation/manifest-check.ts` — AC-003 校验逻辑\n  - [ ] `tests/plugin-api/surface.test.ts` — AC-001..AC-003 单元测试\n- **relates_to**: [F-010, M-007]\n- **context_load**:\n  - arch-wechat-flow-modules#§2.M-007\n  - prd-wechat-flow-f001-f014#§2.F-010\n\n---" .
