<https://cataforge.dev/instance/API-012> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/updated_at> "2026-06-12T04:18:02.18183Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/API-012> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/belongs_to_project> <https://cataforge.dev/instance/proj-default> .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/API-012> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "```yaml\ntool: derive_palette\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002 / F-003 AC-011 / F-010 AC-007\nrequest:\n  body:\n    primary: { type: string, required: true, desc: \"主色（hex / lch / oklch）\" }\n    secondary: { type: string, required: false }\n    accent: { type: string, required: false }\n    dark: { type: boolean, required: false, desc: \"派生暗色梯度\" }\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    tokens: { type: \"Record<string, string>\", desc: \"派生的完整 token 字典\" }\n    wcagWarnings: { type: \"Diagnostic[]\", desc: \"对比度低于 AA 的 token 对警告\" }\n```" .
