<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.5%20%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "ui-spec" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.5%20%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "269b0b42c084c320930a0b2f195b24dd0a52e6f760680098a8898daf1c6b9f25" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.5%20%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000024" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/1.5%20%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%88%20Token> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 1.5 动效 Token\n\n| Token | 值 | 用途 |\n|-------|----|------|\n| `--duration-instant` | `80ms` | 按钮色变、focus ring 出现 |\n| `--duration-fast` | `150ms` | Hover 态切换、Toast 入场 |\n| `--duration-base` | `250ms` | 下拉菜单展开、抽屉展开 |\n| `--duration-slow` | `350ms` | Modal 出场、Command Palette 展开 |\n| `--ease-standard` | `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)` | 大多数 UI 过渡 |\n| `--ease-decelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1)` | 元素入场（从快到慢） |\n| `--ease-accelerate` | `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1)` | 元素退场（从慢到快） |\n\n预览刷新 debounce（来自 Q4 决策）：`300ms`（代码层配置常量 `PREVIEW_DEBOUNCE_MS = 300`，不映射为 CSS Token）。" .
