<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/UC-007%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%88ThemeCard%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "ui-spec" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/UC-007%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%88ThemeCard%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "cccf97788a124083a4eb8981f60020b096421ce0cc8e3c4ae493e4d1a420aafb" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/UC-007%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%88ThemeCard%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000009" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/UC-007%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%88ThemeCard%EF%BC%89> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### UC-007: 主题卡片（ThemeCard）\n\n**映射功能**: F-003 (AC-001 主题选择, AC-003 社区扩展占位)；位于左侧面板「主题」Tab 内\n\n**布局**：卡片尺寸 `宽 (面板宽-2×space-4) × 高 auto`，内部包含主题缩略图（高 `60px`，border-radius `--radius-sm`）+ 主题名（14px, medium）+ 简短描述（12px, muted）。\n\n**状态**：\n\n| 状态 | 视觉表现 |\n|------|---------|\n| `default` | 白色背景卡片（`--color-surface`），边框 `1px solid --color-border-subtle`，无阴影 |\n| `hover` | 背景 `--color-surface-overlay`，边框 `--color-border`，阴影 `--shadow-sm`，鼠标 `pointer` |\n| `selected`（当前应用主题）| 边框 `2px solid --color-brand`，左上角出现对勾图标（`--color-brand`） |\n| `disabled`（占位卡片，如「社区主题」） | 全卡片 opacity `0.6`，缩略图替换为「更多主题即将上线」文字占位，点击跳转 `/themes` 路由 |\n\n**变体 (variant)**: 单一形态组件，无 variant 区分\n\n**Props**: `theme: ThemeDefinition`, `isSelected: boolean`, `isPlaceholder?: boolean`, `onSelect: (id: string) => void`\n\n---" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/ui-spec/sec/UC-007%3A%20%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%8D%A1%E7%89%87%EF%BC%88ThemeCard%EF%BC%89> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/Section> .
