<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-031%3A%20DELETE%20/api/v1/admin/api-keys/%3AkeyId> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "a14180c230aa32a66d8b792aca3a8df1751c2c3a93e02aeecdfd6e35e49bec9f" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-031%3A%20DELETE%20/api/v1/admin/api-keys/%3AkeyId> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000038" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-031%3A%20DELETE%20/api/v1/admin/api-keys/%3AkeyId> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-031: DELETE /api/v1/admin/api-keys/:keyId\n\n```yaml\npath: /api/v1/admin/api-keys/{keyId}\nmethod: DELETE\nmodule: M-010 (admin/api-keys.ts)\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-004\nauth: admin API key\ndesc: \"软删除：标 E-010.revokedAt = now()；不物理删除（保留审计可追溯）\"\nrequest:\n  headers:\n    Authorization: { type: string, required: true }\n    X-Admin-Request: { type: string, required: true }\n  path:\n    keyId: { type: string, required: true }\nresponse:\n  204:\n    desc: \"吊销成功，无 body\"\n  401: { schema: ErrorResponse }\n  403: { schema: ErrorResponse }\n  404: { schema: ErrorResponse, desc: \"E_NOT_FOUND — keyId 不存在\" }\n  409: { schema: ErrorResponse, desc: \"E_CONFLICT — 该 key 已被 revoke\" }\n```" .
