<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.5%20%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/source_doc> "prd" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.5%20%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/content_hash> "41a424ccd655f022efab64086d738c23445ad3a25412d8795d7f7a0d0c860be4" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.5%20%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000011" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/prd/sec/3.5%20%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%AA%8C%E6%94%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### 3.5 视觉一致性验收规范\n\n视觉一致性 ≤ 5% 的验收口径在三个层级统一定义，避免 CI 门禁与发布前人工验证边界混淆。\n\n| 层级 | 验收路径 | 频次 | 通过条件 |\n|------|---------|------|---------|\n| CI 默认门禁 | 本地 Playwright + 渲染管线 `simulatePaste` 模拟（不调用真实公众号） | 每 PR | pixelmatch ratio ≤ 0.05；详见 F-011 AC-004a |\n| 发布前周期验证 | 真实公众号编辑器粘贴 → 截图回归 | 每 minor release 前 | 5 主题 × 1 篇典型样本视觉差异 ≤ 5%；结果回写 `docs/EVENT-LOG.jsonl` |\n| 紧急回归排查 | 实地验证辅助脚本生成对照页 | 按需触发 | 见 F-011 AC-008 |\n\n共享参数（与 §4 [ASSUMPTION] 一致）：算法 `pixelmatch` (threshold 0.2, includeAA: false)；视口 1280×800 (desktop) + 375×667 (mobile)；5 篇典型样本固定在 `tests/visual/samples/{theme}/article.md`（5 主题 × 1 篇）；计算口径 `mismatched_pixels / total_pixels ≤ 0.05`。\n\n---" .
