<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-006%3A%20describe_block> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-006: describe_block\n\n```yaml\ntool: describe_block\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002 / F-010 AC-004\nrequest:\n  body:\n    blockId: { type: string, required: true }\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    id: { type: string }\n    name: { type: string }\n    attrsSchema: { type: \"JSONSchema\", desc: \"Block 属性的 JSON Schema 表达，便于 LLM 生成合法 Markdown\" }\n    variants: { type: \"VariantSummary[]\" }\n    tokenDependencies: { type: \"string[]\", desc: \"该 Block 消费的 token 路径\" }\n```" .
