<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/arch/sec/API-010%3A%20list_block_variants> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "#### API-010: list_block_variants\n\n```yaml\ntool: list_block_variants\nmodule: M-009\nmaps_to: F-013 AC-002 / F-003 AC-007\nrequest:\n  body:\n    blockId: { type: string, required: true }\nresponse:\n  schema:\n    variants: { type: \"VariantSummary[]\", desc: \"{id, name, themeAffinity?: string[], description}[]\" }\n```" .
