<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-101%3A%20%5BDESIGN%5D%20Penpot%20%E2%80%94%20Sprint%203%20%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%A8%BF%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/position> "000013" .
<https://cataforge.dev/instance/doc/dev-plan/sec/T-101%3A%20%5BDESIGN%5D%20Penpot%20%E2%80%94%20Sprint%203%20%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%A8%BF%E7%AD%BE%E5%AD%97%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81> <https://cataforge.dev/ontology/narrative_body> "### T-101: [DESIGN] Penpot — Sprint 3 设计稿签字验证\n\n- **目标**: 开发者/PM 目视检查 Sprint 3 UI 实现（主题切换、LeftPanelTabs、CommandPalette）与 Penpot 设计稿的一致性，完成 sign-off\n- **task_kind**: design\n- **tdd_acceptance**: skip\n- **priority**: P1\n- **complexity**: small\n- **sprint**: 3\n- **tdd_mode**: skip\n- **tdd_skip_reason**: \"Penpot 设计稿，由用户视觉验证 sign-off\"\n- **dependencies**: [T-100]\n- **acceptance_criteria**:\n  - [ ] AC-001: 目视对照 Penpot UC-009 CommandPalette `open-results` 状态与实际 UI，分组标题字号/颜色/快捷键提示布局无明显偏差\n  - [ ] AC-002: 目视对照 Penpot UC-007 ThemeCard `selected` 状态与实际 UI，边框色 `--color-brand` 和对勾图标可见\n  - [ ] AC-003: 签字记录写入 `docs/EVENT-LOG.jsonl`（`event=design_signoff, phase=development, ref=T-101`）\n- **deliverables**:\n  - [ ] `docs/EVENT-LOG.jsonl` — design_signoff 事件（T-101）\n\n---" .
